        "TileImage": "$($repository c823beec-3d73-47b6-87d9-076c384c4662).Image",
        "Description": "The Epstein Files have exposed a sex slave operation in Italy. Padre Francesco is the ringleader, and a sadist. Take him out and dawn the holy cloth he has besmirched. Visit vengence dressed as an archangel of wrath upon his co-conspiraters. Andrea Penca, a man with a drinking problem and a penchant for violence. Stefano Zelaschi, he snatches unsuspecting victims from schoolyards and playgrounds. Fabio Pavione can make anyone disappear for good. You will find him in his mortuary of debauchery.",
